            <h3>State-of-the-Art Facilities</h3>
            <p>Aatura Hospital is equipped with advanced technology and state-of-the-art facilities to support our Pain Management Department's efforts. From our procedure rooms and imaging suites to our rehabilitation gym and relaxation areas, we have the resources needed to provide comprehensive pain management services in a comfortable and supportive environment.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content3">
        <div class="cl">
            <h3>Patient-Centered Care</h3>
            <p>At Aatura Hospital, we prioritize patient-centered care, focusing on the individual needs and concerns of each patient. Our pain management specialists take the time to listen to patients' experiences, understand their goals and preferences, and involve them in decision-making regarding their treatment plan. We believe in fostering a collaborative and trusting relationship with our patients to optimize outcomes and improve quality of life.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content4">
